spreader board
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a board fitted at the rear of a konaki, sledge or trailer, for the even spreading of animal manure on to paddocks.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
